itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome back Rock musician Barns Courtney to discuss the success of his recent album “404”, how he is fairing during the quarantine in England, talk about what would happen if Michael Jackson was invited onto “MTV Cribs”, Barns describes recording during Quarantimes, and Ross and Dan have both have agreed to adopt Barns Courtney and become his parents.
